#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Intangiriro"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module is designed to help users who have difficulty hearing audible "
"cues, or who have difficulty using a keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Modire ni Kuri Ifashayobora Abakoresha , Cyangwa ikoresha A Mwandikisho . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The module is divided into six tabs: <link linkend=\"access-bell"
"\"><guilabel>Bell</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-modifier-keys"
"\"><guilabel>Modifier keys</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-"
"keyboard-filters\"><guilabel>Keyboard Filters</guilabel></link>, <link "
"linkend=\"access-activation-gestures\"><guilabel>Activation Gestures</"
"guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"mouse-navigation\"><guilabel>Mouse "
"Navigation</guilabel></link>, and <link linkend=\"access-screenreader"
"\"><guilabel>Screen Reader</guilabel></link>."
msgstr ""
"Modire ni Kabiri Amasimbuka : <link linkend=\"access-bell\"> <guilabel> </"
"guilabel> </link> na "

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Bell"
msgstr "Inzogera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This panel is divided into an <guilabel>Audible Bell</guilabel> section and "
"a <guilabel>Visible Bell</guilabel> section."
msgstr ""
"Umwanya ni <guilabel> </guilabel> Icyiciro na A <guilabel> </guilabel> "
"Icyiciro . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top check box labeled <guilabel>Use System Bell</guilabel>, determines "
"whether the normal System bell rings. If this option is disabled, the System "
"bell will be silenced."
msgstr ""
"Hejuru: Kugenzura Agasanduku <guilabel> </guilabel> , i Bisanzwe &Inzogera "
"Impeta . iyi Ihitamo ni Yahagaritswe , i &Inzogera . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next check box down can be used to play a different sound whenever the "
"system bell is triggered. To activate, place a mark in the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Use customized bell</guilabel>, and enter the complete pathname to "
"the sound file in the text box labeled <guilabel>Sound to play</guilabel>. "
"If you want, you can select the <guibutton>Browse</guibutton> button to "
"navigate through your filesystem to find the exact file."
msgstr ""
"Ibikurikira > Kugenzura Agasanduku Hasi Byakoreshejwe Kuri Gukina A Ijwi i "
"Sisitemu &Inzogera ni . Kureka bigakora , A Ikimenyetso in i Kugenzura "
"Agasanduku <guilabel> Kunozwa &Inzogera </guilabel> , na Injiza i Byuzuye "
"Kuri i Ijwi Idosiye in i Umwandiko Agasanduku <guilabel> Kuri </"
"guilabel> . , Guhitamo i <guibutton> </guibutton> Akabuto Kuri Kubuganya "
"Gihinguranya Kuri Gushaka i NYACYO Idosiye . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For those users who have difficulty hearing the System bell, or those users "
"who have a silent computer, &kde; offers the <emphasis>visual bell</"
"emphasis>. This provides a visual signal (inverting the screen or flashing a "
"color across it) when the system bell would normally sound."
msgstr ""
"Abakoresha i &Inzogera , Cyangwa Abakoresha A , &kde; i <emphasis> "
"Kigaragara &Inzogera </emphasis> . A Kigaragara ( i Mugaragaza Cyangwa A "
"Ibara: Kwambukiranya ) Ryari: i Sisitemu &Inzogera Ijwi . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use the visual bell, first place a mark in the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Use visual bell</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Koresha i Kigaragara &Inzogera , Itangira A Ikimenyetso in i Kugenzura "
"Agasanduku <guilabel> Kigaragara &Inzogera </guilabel> . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then select between <guilabel>Invert screen</guilabel>, or "
"<guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel>. If you select <guilabel>Invert screen</"
"guilabel>, all colors on the screen will be reversed. If you choose "
"<guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel>, you can choose the color by clicking the "
"button to the right of the <guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel> selection."
msgstr ""
"Hanyuma Guhitamo hagati <guilabel> Mugaragaza </guilabel> , Cyangwa "
"<guilabel> Mugaragaza </guilabel> . Guhitamo <guilabel> Mugaragaza </"
"guilabel> , Byose Amabara ku i Mugaragaza Bicuritswe . Hitamo... <guilabel> "
"Mugaragaza </guilabel> , Hitamo... i Ibara: ku i Akabuto Kuri i Iburyo: Bya "
"i <guilabel> Mugaragaza </guilabel> Ihitamo . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The spin box can be used to adjust the duration of the visible bell. The "
"default value is 500 msec, or half a second."
msgstr ""
"Umurongo Byakoreshejwe Kuri i Igihe-ngombwa Bya i Kigaragara &Inzogera . "
"Mburabuzi Agaciro: ni , Cyangwa A ISEGONDA . "

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier keys"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are the two sections <guilabel>Sticky Keys</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Locking Keys</guilabel> to this panel."
msgstr ""
"Umwanya ni <guilabel> </guilabel> Icyiciro na A <guilabel> </guilabel> "
"Icyiciro . "

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:107
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Use Sticky Keys"
msgstr "Gukoresha buto zifashe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you can press and release the &Shift;, &Alt; or "
"&Ctrl; keys, and then press another key to get a key combo (example: "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Del;</keycombo> could be done with "
"&Ctrl;, then &Alt; and then &Del;)."
msgstr ""
"iyi Ihitamo ni Bikora , i Umukoresha Kanda na Irekura: i &Shift; , &Alt; "
"Cyangwa &Ctrl; Utubuto , na Hanyuma Kanda Urufunguzo Kuri Kubona A "
"Urufunguzo ( Urugero: : <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl; &Alt; <keycap> </"
"keycap> </keycombo> Byakozwe Na: &Ctrl; Hanyuma &Alt; Hanyuma <keycap> </"
"keycap> ) . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also in this section is a check box labeled <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</"
"guilabel>. If this check box is enabled, the &Alt;, &Ctrl; and &Shift; keys "
"stay <quote>selected</quote> until you <quote>de-selected</quote> them."
msgstr ""
"in iyi Icyiciro ni A Kugenzura Agasanduku <guilabel> </guilabel> . iyi "
"Kugenzura Agasanduku ni Bikora , i &Alt; , &Ctrl; na &Shift; Utubuto <quote> "
"Byahiswemo </quote> &Kugeza <quote> - Byahiswemo </quote> ku i Umukoresha . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "As an example:"
msgstr "Urugero: : "

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:128
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "With <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</guilabel> disabled:"
msgstr "<guilabel> </guilabel> Yahagaritswe : "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press the &Shift; key then press the <keycap>F</keycap> key, the "
"computer interprets this as <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</"
"keycap></keycombo>. Now if you type a <keycap>P</keycap>, the computer "
"interprets this as the letter p (no shift)."
msgstr ""
"Umukoresha i &Shift; Urufunguzo , Hanyuma i <keycap> </keycap> Urufunguzo . "
"iyi <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Shift; <keycap> </keycap> </keycombo> . "
"NIBA i Umukoresha A <keycap> p </keycap> , i iyi Nka i Ibaruwa: p ( Oya "
"Gusunika ) . "

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:140
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "With <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</guilabel> enabled:"
msgstr "<guilabel> </guilabel> Bikora : "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press the &Shift; key <emphasis>twice</emphasis> then press the "
"<keycap>F</keycap> key, the computer interprets this as <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Now if you type a <keycap>P</"
"keycap>, the computer interprets this as the letter P (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>). To de-select the &Shift; "
"key, press it again."
msgstr ""
"Umukoresha i &Shift; Urufunguzo , Hanyuma i <keycap> </keycap> Urufunguzo . "
"iyi <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Shift; <keycap> </keycap> </keycombo> . "
"NIBA i Umukoresha A <keycap> p </keycap> , i iyi Nka i Ibaruwa: ( <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"> &Shift; <keycap> </keycap> </keycombo> ) . "

