#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:183
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Use slow keys"
msgstr "Buto zigenda Buhoro"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you must hold the key down for a specified length "
"of time (adjustable with the spin box) before the keystroke will be "
"accepted. This helps prevent accidental key strokes."
msgstr ""
"iyi Ihitamo ni Bikora , i Umukoresha Gufata i Urufunguzo Hasi ya:  A Igihe "
"Bya Igihe ( Na: i ) Mbere i Byemewe . Urufunguzo . "

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:196
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Use bounce keys"
msgstr "Buto Zidunda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you must wait for a specified length of time "
"(configurable with the spin box) before the next key press can be accepted. "
"This prevents accidental multiple key strokes."
msgstr ""
"iyi Ihitamo ni Bikora , i Umukoresha Tegereza A Gutinda ( Na: i ) Mbere i "
"Ibikurikira > Urufunguzo Kanda Byemewe . Igikubo Urufunguzo . "

